OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan raises age of consent
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom 13 to 16              
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Japan has passed laws that redefine    
OL,6, rape and raise the age of consent in a 
OL,7, landmark overhaul of sex crime laws.   
OL,9,FThe definition of rape was broadened to
OL,10,F"non-consensual sexual intercourse"    
OL,11,Ffrom "forcible sexual intercourse",    
OL,12,Faligning Japanese law's definition with
OL,13,Fother countries.                       
OL,15,FThe legal age of consent, previously at
OL,16,Fonly 13, has been raised to 16 years.  
OL,18,FPrevious laws did not protect those    
OL,19,Fcoerced into having sex and deterred   
OL,20,Freporting of such attacks, critics say.
